Keith Wayne https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keith_Wayne 0 Keith Wayne (January 16, 1945 — September 9, 1995), born Ronald Keith Hartman, was an American actor known for his (only) role as Tom in the George A. Romero film Night of the Living Dead (1968).
